item.title: CVE-2023-0892|2024-08-02T05:24:34.724Z -- unknown -- bizlibrary
item.description: The BizLibrary WordPress plugin through 1.1 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup)
